{"tid":1180564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不知教授猝逝    忠犬仍天天到學校苦等","createTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T09:51:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1347,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"c967872e660298fe41fe879370e96102ac39c822","tid":1180564,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"菲律賓邦板牙省馬巴拉卡特學院（Mabalacat City College）最近幾個禮拜以來，都可以看到一隻狗狗在教師休息室前苦等的身影，讓許多人都為之鼻酸。原來這裡的一位教授馬塞洛（Carmelito Marcelo）非常疼愛這隻叫做Buboy的狗狗，每天來學校上課時都會摸摸牠、餵牠吃東西。然而馬塞洛二週前突然因為心臟病而不幸離世，毫不知情的Buboy仍然每天到學校等待好友，忠心模樣令人心疼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2VjktI4wh46GbEPSy6pUDQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDQ1/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/nownews.com/228672395587c037ace68666a62d8276\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2VjktI4wh46GbEPSy6pUDQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDQ1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fnownews.com%2F228672395587c037ace68666a62d8276&h=e28a701d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬塞洛和Buboy感情相當好，Buboy每天都會到學校去找馬塞洛，對牠來說，馬塞洛可能像是爸爸或好友一般的存在。（圖／FB@Ma Kristina Paola Demafelix）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而天有不測風雲，二週前馬塞洛因為心臟不適住院，最後沒能撐過去。不知道好友已經離世的Buboy仍舊每天到教師休息室門口等待，卻再也見不到馬塞洛的身影。<br />\n<br />\n學校職員克莉絲汀娜不忍心看Buboy一直苦等，決定帶著牠一起參加馬塞洛的告別式，讓Buboy可以跟馬塞洛好好告別。沒想到Buboy在趴棺看完馬塞洛的最後一面後，就在棺木旁躺了下來，不願離開，似乎是知道一旦離開就再也見不到好友，讓現場的眾人都十分心疼及感動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Da9V9O7pbIUl.AQk2Y8B1Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/nownews.com/a69f23cb8bd1a5228849382323408f22\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDa9V9O7pbIUl.AQk2Y8B1Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fnownews.com%2Fa69f23cb8bd1a5228849382323408f22&h=b3cd1872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在學校職員克莉絲汀娜的協助之下，Buboy在告別式上見到了好友馬塞洛的最後一面。（圖／FB@Ma Kristina Paola Demafelix）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/O1NIwUg4NUvL.GvN45aH1Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/nownews.com/07636bfb369c4c559af64c00ba18fa42\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FO1NIwUg4NUvL.GvN45aH1Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fnownews.com%2F07636bfb369c4c559af64c00ba18fa42&h=2a9816ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒想到Buboy就這樣在馬塞洛的棺木旁躺了下來，不願意離開。（圖／FB@Ma Kristina Paola Demafelix）<br />\n<br />\n在告別式之後，Buboy似乎是認知了馬塞洛已經不在的事實，不再到教師休息室門口苦等。現在學校的教職員自動自發開始共同照顧Buboy，雖然失去了好友，但Buboy仍舊有許多人的關愛，相信馬塞洛在天之靈也可以放心了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%B2%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%8C%9D%E9%80%9D-%E5%BF%A0%E7%8A%AC%E4%BB%8D%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%88%B0%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E8%8B%A6%E7%AD%89%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%9C%BE%E4%BA%BA-091212999.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E7%258C%259D%25E9%2580%259D-%25E5%25BF%25A0%25E7%258A%25AC%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%258B%25A6%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259C%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA-091212999.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=4424cc31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%B2%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%8C%9D%E9%80%9D-%E5%BF%A0%E7%8A%AC%E4%BB%8D%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A9%E5%88%B0%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E8%8B%A6%E7%AD%89%E6%84%9F%E5%8B%95%E7%9C%BE%E4%BA%BA-091212999.html</a>"},{"pid":"87941741b150bc46b8d3ac34a1d606e59c653a2c","tid":1180564,"uid":141151,"like":377,"dislike":1,"score":376,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c